Products.description: An all-new glass design, an updated camera, and a powerful chip, there's so much to love about the iPhone 9. This iPhone brings you an augmented reality experience that's more immersive than before. What's more? You can charge your iPhone wirelessly!

Products.title: iPhone X
Products.subTitle: APPLE iPhone X (Space Gray, 64 GB)
Products.description: Meet the iPhone X - the device that's so smart that it responds to a tap, your voice, and even a glance. Elegantly designed with a large 14.73 cm (5.8) Super Retina screen and a durable front-and-back glass, this smartphone is designed to impress. What's more, you can charge this iPhone wirelessly.

Products.title: Samsung Galaxy F13
Products.subTitle: SAMSUNG Galaxy F13 (Waterfall Blue, 64 GB)(4 GB RAM)
Products.description: Enjoy seamless connectivity and an uninterrupted movie marathon with the impressive Samsung Galaxy F13 that is designed specifically to impress the entertainment fanatics. This smartphone features a terrific 16.62 cm (6.6) FHD+ LCD Display that can effortlessly blow your mind with its incredible performance. Furthermore, this phone boasts a 50 MP Triple Camera setup that allows you to capture awesomeness with a gentle tap. Moreover, the Samsung Galaxy F13 sports up to 8 GB of RAM and features an innovative RAM plus technology that taps into the phone’s internal storage to elevate its performance.

Products.description: The OPPO F19 is a smartphone designed and created to match your dynamic and stylish lifestyle. This smartphone features a 5000 mAh Battery for uninterrupted use, an AMOLED FHD+ Punch-hole Display for clear visuals, and an AI Beautification Selfie Camera to capture striking selfies with every click.

Products.title: Huawei P30
Products.subTitle: Huawei P30 Lite (Peacock Blue, 128 GB)
Products.description: The Huawei features a 6000 mAh battery to ensure that you get your fill of productivity and entertainment. Its 16.56cm (6.52) HD+ Full View Dew Drop Display gives you an expansive view and immersive experience while streaming content, gaming, video calling your loved ones, and more. You can stay connected at all times as this mobile phone offers up to 34 days of standby, 60 hours of calling, and much more.
